---
import ArrowIcon from './ArrowIcon.astro';
---

<div class="exposure-sheet">
  <div class="exposure-inputs">
    <p class="data-label">Illustrative inputs · not a valuation</p>
    <div class="input-row"><span>Employees in the group</span><strong>12</strong></div>
    <div class="input-row"><span>Estimated weekly gap</span><strong>2.5 hr</strong></div>
    <div class="input-row"><span>Average regular rate</span><strong>$28.00</strong></div>
    <div class="input-row"><span>Lookback</span><strong>3 yr</strong></div>
  </div>
  <div class="exposure-result">
    <p class="data-label">Wages-only orientation</p>
    <strong class="amount">$131,040</strong>
    <p>Estimated straight-time wages represented by those inputs. Penalties, interest, fees, taxes, premiums, and factual defenses are excluded.</p>
    <a href="/tools/exposure-snapshot/">Use your own inputs <ArrowIcon /></a>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .exposure-sheet { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 5fr) minmax(20rem, 7fr); border: 2px solid var(--color-ink); }
  .exposure-inputs, .exposure-result { padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem); }
  .exposure-inputs { background: var(--color-paper-blue); }
  .input-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; border-top: var(--rule); padding-block: 0.9rem; }
  .input-row:last-child { border-bottom: var(--rule); }
  .input-row span { color: var(--color-muted); }
  .input-row strong { color: var(--color-ink); font-family: var(--font-mono); }
  .exposure-result { display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; border-left: 2px solid var(--color-ink); }
  .amount { display: block; color: var(--color-cobalt); font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(3.7rem, 8vw, 7.5rem); font-variation-settings: 'wdth' 82; letter-spacing: -0.06em; line-height: 0.9; }
  .exposure-result > p:not(.data-label) { max-width: 35rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; color: var(--color-muted); }
  a { display: inline-flex; width: fit-content; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; color: var(--color-cobalt-dark); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
  @media (max-width: 48rem) { .exposure-sheet { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .exposure-result { border-top: 2px solid var(--color-ink); border-left: 0; } }
</style>
